an</a></td></tr>  <tr class="odd"><td class="hs"><a href="http://pro.imdb.com/widget/resume_redirect/" onClick="(new Image()).src='/rg/resume/prosystem/images/b.gif?link=http://pro.imdb.com/widget/resume_redirect/';"><img src="http://i.media-imdb.com/images/SF9113d6f5b7cb1533c35313ccd181a6b1/tn15/no_photo.png" width="25" height="31" border="0"></td><td class="nm"><a href="/name/nm0786022/" onclick="(new Image()).src='/rg/castlist/position-15/images/b.gif?link=/name/nm0786022/';">Roshan Seth</a></td><td class="ddd"> ... </td><td class="char">Pandit Nehru</td></tr>  <tr class="even"><td class="hs"><a href="http://pro.imdb.com/widget/resume_redirect/" onClick="(new Image()).src='/rg/resume/prosystem/images/b.gif?link=http://pro.imdb.com/widget/resume_redirect/';"><img src="http://i.media-imdb.com/images/SF9113d6f5b7cb1533c35313ccd181a6b1/tn15/no_photo.png" width="25" height="31" border="0"></td><td class="nm"><a href="/name/nm0368990/" onclick="(new Image()).src='/rg/castlist/position-16/images/b.gif?link=/name/nm0368990/';">Rohini Hattangadi</a></td><td class="ddd"> ... </td><td class="char"><a href="/character/ch0035616/">Kasturba Gandhi</a> (as Rohini Hattangady)</td></tr>  <tr class="odd"><td class="hs"><a href="/name/nm0000846/" onClick="(new Image()).src='/rg/title-tease/tinyhead/images/b.gif?link=/name/nm0000846/';"><img src="http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/M/MV5BMTI4NDQyMDU4NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTYwMTk3OTU3._V1._SY30_SX23_.jpg" width="23" height="32" border="0"></a><br></td><td class="nm"><a href="/name/nm0000846/" onclick="(new Image()).src='/rg/castlist/position-17/images/b.gif?link=/name/nm0000846/';">Ian Bannen</a></td><td class="ddd"> ... </td><td class="char">Senior Police Officer</td></tr>  <tr class="even"><td class="hs"><a href="http://pro.imdb.com/widget/resume_redirect/" onClick="(new Image()).src='/rg/resume/prosystem/images/b.gif?link=http://pro.imdb.com/widget/resume_redirect/';"><img src="http://i.media-imdb.com/images/SF9113d6f5b7cb1533c35313ccd181a6